---
type Props = {
  canonEntryCount: number;
  mappedEventCount: number;
};

const { canonEntryCount, mappedEventCount } = Astro.props;
---

<div class="home-gateway" id="home-gateway-top">
  <section class="home-hero" aria-labelledby="home-hero-title">
    <div class="home-hero__copy">
      <p class="home-eyebrow">Choose an age. Enter the same world.</p>
      <h1 id="home-hero-title">VISCERIUM</h1>
      <p class="home-hero__deck">One timeline. Four eras. Infinite stories.</p>
      <div class="home-actions">
        <a class="home-button" href="/start-here/">Start here</a>
        <a class="home-button home-button--secondary" href="#home-era-gateway">Explore the four eras</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <ol class="home-era-gateway" id="home-era-gateway" aria-label="The four eras of VISCERIUM">
      <li>
        <a class="home-era-card home-era-card--citadel" href="/eras/citadel/" aria-describedby="home-citadel-description">
          <div class="home-era-card__content">
            <span class="home-era-card__number">Era I</span>
            <h2>CITADEL</h2>
            <p class="home-era-card__tags">Steel · Bone · Early gunpowder</p>
            <p class="home-era-card__description" id="home-citadel-description">A medieval age of walled realms, ritualised Resonance and horrors still mistaken for folklore.</p>
            <span class="home-era-card__action">Explore CITADEL</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a class="home-era-card home-era-card--smog" href="/eras/smog/" aria-describedby="home-smog-description">
          <div class="home-era-card__content">
            <span class="home-era-card__number">Era II</span>
            <h2>SMOG</h2>
            <p class="home-era-card__tags">Industry · Trenches · Occult machinery</p>
            <p class="home-era-card__description" id="home-smog-description">Civilisation industrialises its wars faster than it learns from them, filling the old world with soot, engines and inherited grief.</p>
            <span class="home-era-card__action">Explore SMOG</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a class="home-era-card home-era-card--nearsight" href="/eras/nearsight/" aria-describedby="home-nearsight-description">
          <div class="home-era-card__content">
            <span class="home-era-card__number">Era III</span>
            <h2>NEARSIGHT</h2>
            <p class="home-era-card__tags">Satellites · Exoskeletons · Cassette futurism</p>
            <p class="home-era-card__description" id="home-nearsight-description">Humanity believes the world is finally observable while the real enemy remains beyond its field of view.</p>
            <span class="home-era-card__action">Explore NEARSIGHT</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a class="home-era-card home-era-card--entropy" href="/eras/entropy/" aria-describedby="home-entropy-description">
          <div class="home-era-card__content">
            <span class="home-era-card__number">Era IV</span>
            <h2>ENTROPY</h2>
            <p class="home-era-card__tags">Orbital war · Altered flesh · Extinction</p>
            <p class="home-era-card__description" id="home-entropy-description">The old struggle escapes Errack and reveals the scale of what has always surrounded the Degel System.</p>
            <span class="home-era-card__action">Explore ENTROPY</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </section>

  <section class="home-section" id="home-continuum" aria-labelledby="home-continuum-title">
    <div class="home-section__grid">
      <header>
        <p class="home-eyebrow">One wounded history</p>
        <h2 class="home-section__heading" id="home-continuum-title">The world advances. The struggle does not.</h2>
        <p class="home-lead">VISCERIUM follows one secondary world across millennia rather than resetting the setting whenever its technology changes.</p>
      </header>
      <div class="home-body-copy">
        <p>Kingdoms become republics. Rituals become sciences. Old superstitions survive inside military doctrine, industry and orbital infrastructure. Resonance, incursion and mortal ambition remain the connective tissue.</p>
        <p>The four gateways above are not separate universes. They are four moments in the same history, each carrying the damage, discoveries and lies of the age before it.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <figure class="home-timeline">
      <div class="home-timeline__viewport" tabindex="0" role="region" aria-label="Scrollable VISCERIUM technology timeline">
        <ol class="home-tech-timeline">
          <li class="home-tech-era home-tech-era--citadel">
            <span class="home-tech-era__index">I</span>
            <strong>CITADEL</strong>
            <span>Steel, siegecraft and early gunpowder</span>
          </li>
          <li class="home-tech-era home-tech-era--smog">
            <span class="home-tech-era__index">II</span>
            <strong>SMOG</strong>
            <span>Industry, combustion and mechanised war</span>
          </li>
          <li class="home-tech-era home-tech-era--nearsight">
            <span class="home-tech-era__index">III</span>
            <strong>NEARSIGHT</strong>
            <span>Networks, robotics and near-orbital reach</span>
          </li>
          <li class="home-tech-era home-tech-era--entropy">
            <span class="home-tech-era__index">IV</span>
            <strong>ENTROPY</strong>
            <span>Vacuum warfare, altered flesh and deep space</span>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
      <figcaption>Technology advances continuously across the four eras. On narrow screens, swipe or use the arrow keys while this timeline is focused.</figcaption>
    </figure>
  </section>

  <section class="home-section" id="home-statistics" aria-labelledby="home-statistics-title">
    <header class="home-section__intro">
      <p class="home-eyebrow">The living archive</p>
      <h2 class="home-section__heading" id="home-statistics-title">A world measured by what has survived.</h2>
      <p class="home-lead">The Codex grows from published canon. These figures are calculated from the live archive whenever the site builds.</p>
    </header>

    <dl class="home-stats">
      <div class="home-stat"><dd>4</dd><dt>Distinct eras</dt></div>
      <div class="home-stat"><dd>{canonEntryCount}</dd><dt>Canon entries</dt></div>
      <div class="home-stat"><dd>{mappedEventCount}</dd><dt>Mapped events</dt></div>
      <div class="home-stat"><dd>1</dd><dt>Unbroken timeline</dt></div>
    </dl>
  </section>

  <section class="home-section" id="home-routes" aria-labelledby="home-routes-title">
    <header class="home-section__intro">
      <p class="home-eyebrow">Suggested entry routes</p>
      <h2 class="home-section__heading" id="home-routes-title">Go deeper with context.</h2>
      <p class="home-lead">The spectacle gets attention. These curated records prevent a new reader from becoming lost in the archive.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="home-route-grid">
      <a class="home-route-card" href="/start-here/">
        <span class="home-route-card__symbol" aria-hidden="true">Ⅰ</span>
        <h3>Start Here</h3>
        <p>The essential primer to VISCERIUM, the Degel System and its four eras.</p>
        <strong>Recommended first</strong>
      </a>
      <a class="home-route-card" href="/degel-system/degel/">
        <span class="home-route-card__symbol" aria-hidden="true">⌁</span>
        <h3>The Degel System</h3>
        <p>Begin with the star system whose worlds, wounds and hidden structures contain the greater struggle.</p>
        <strong>Enter the setting</strong>
      </a>
      <a class="home-route-card" href="/timelines/super/">
        <span class="home-route-card__symbol" aria-hidden="true">✣</span>
        <h3>The Timeline</h3>
        <p>Follow the inherited events that connect CITADEL, SMOG, NEARSIGHT and ENTROPY.</p>
        <strong>Trace the history</strong>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="home-final-cta" aria-labelledby="home-start-title">
    <div class="home-section home-final-cta__inner">
      <p class="home-eyebrow">The first article</p>
      <h2 class="home-section__heading" id="home-start-title">Begin before the names become weapons.</h2>
      <p class="home-lead">Enter VISCERIUM through the guided primer, then choose an age.</p>
      <div class="home-actions">
        <a class="home-button" href="/start-here/">Read Start Here</a>
        <a class="home-button home-button--secondary" href="#home-gateway-top">Return to the gateways</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
